{"id":5247,"count":14,"description":"<h2>Middle East<\/h2>\r\nThe Middle East: a place of historical legend, home to some of the oldest, and most spectacular, places on the planet! Prepare to see the past come to life, discovering ancient ruins, lost cities, and the unforgettable sight of the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/egypt\/cairo\/\">Egyptian pyramids<\/a>. The Middle East effortlessly balances this incredible past, whilst pushing into new realms of the future. As a result, Middle-Eastern cities are astonishing places, where dazzling luxuriousness is commonplace. Be blown away by the tallest building in the world in Dubai or stunning retreats in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/oman\/\">Oman<\/a>. Despite this wealth, the simplicity of nature is never far away. Here, turtles, dolphins, and beautiful corals thrive in the warm ocean, making it a favorite for scuba-divers worldwide.\r\n<h3>Burning Desert Sands<\/h3>\r\nThe Middle East dreams in color: in the reds, oranges, and yellows of wonderful textiles, aromatic spices, burning desert sands, and flaming skies. These warm desert landscapes, incredible canyons, and formations, continue to inspire movie epics and stories. However, the Middle East is not just sizzling heat and desert. It is also home to lush scenery, such as rolling green mountains, fields of pretty wildflowers, and beautiful turquoise blue pools. This contrast means there is something for everyone in the Middle East. Be it floating in the salty Dead Sea, hiking in magnificent mountains, or admiring fascinating Egyptian hieroglyphs and murals.\r\n<h3>Arabian Nights<\/h3>\r\nThe stories of 'Arabian nights' come alive in this mystical, and enchanting region. The themes of fate and destiny are most present on nights stargazing in the desert, an experience unlike any other. It\u2019s no wonder the Middle East is the birthplace of incredible folktales and legends. These stories are often told by beautiful, local people, who are a